articles.headline: AAC taking postseason hoops tourneys to Birmingham, Tampa

images.name: American Athletic Conference logo [1296x729]
images.credit: Cal Sport Media via AP Images

articles.description: The American Athletic Conference is taking its postseason basketball tournaments to Birmingham, Alabama, and Tampa, Florida, over the next three seasons after a five-year run in Texas.
